Hi Parent_C—happy to share more detail.

1) **Daily schedule & outdoor time**
- **Arrival & settling-in:** calm drop-off, choice play/centers

- **Staggered/gradual start** when possible (shorter initial days)
- A consistent **primary point-of-contact teacher** to build trust
- Predictable routines + visual cues (simple “what comes next” structure)
- Regular parent check-ins in the first weeks; we adjust pacing if separation is tough

**Key steps/dates if you apply later**
- The main step is simply **sending an application message when you’re ready**. If you’d like, I can also note your interest so we can move quickly if a spot aligns.
